h snapshots\nare sent during rebalancing, reducing network/IO impact but slowing rebalance\noperations. This is a deliberate non-default tuning.\n\nNOTE: diagnostics.reporting.enabled = true means anonymous diagnostics are\nreported to Cockroach Labs. Confirm this is acceptable per your data policy.\n\nNOTE: sql.defaults.* settings all remain at their default values (no overrides\ndetected). Specifically verified: sql.defaults.distsql, sql.defaults.serial_normalization,\nand related session-defaults are not customized.\n\n3. ZONE CONFIGURATIONS\n-----------------------\nSource: crdb_internal.zones\n\n  Target                                        | num_replicas | gc.ttlseconds | range_min_bytes | range_max_bytes\n  ----------------------------------------------|-------------|---------------|-----------------|----------------\n  RANGE default                                 | 3           | 14400 (4h)    | 128 MiB         | 512 MiB\n  DATABASE system                               | 5           | 14400 (4h)    | 128 MiB         | 512 MiB\n  RANGE meta                                    | 5           | 3600 (1h)     | 128 MiB         | 512 MiB\n  RANGE system                                  | 5           | 14400 (4h)    | 128 MiB         | 512 MiB\n  RANGE liveness                                | 5           | 600 (10m)     | 128 MiB         | 512 MiB\n  TABLE system.public.lease                     | (inherited) | 600 (10m)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\n  TABLE system.public.replication_constraint_stats | (inherited) | 600 (10m)  | (inherited)     | (inherited)\n  TABLE system.public.replication_stats         | (inherited) | 600 (10m)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\n  TABLE system.public.statement_statistics      | (inherited) | 3600 (1h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\n  TABLE system.public.transaction_statistics    | (inherited) | 3600 (1h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\n  TABLE system.public.tenant_usage              | (inherited) | 7200 (2h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\n  TABLE system.public.span_stats_tenant_boundaries | (inherited) | 3600 (1h)  | (inherited)     | (inherited)\n  TABLE system.public.statement_activity        | (inherited) | 3600 (1h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\n  TABLE system.public.transaction_activity      | (inherited) | 3600 (1h)     | (inherited)     | (inherited)\n\n4. REPLICATION FACTOR SUMMARY\n-------------------------------\n  - User data (RANGE default): num_replicas = 3\n  - System ranges (meta, system, liveness, DATABASE system): num_replicas = 5\n  - No custom replication zones applied to user databases/tables (only system ranges)\n\n5. GC TTL SUMMARY\n------------------\n  - Default range GC TTL:  14400 seconds (4 hours)\n  - RANGE meta GC TTL:     3600 seconds (1 hour)\n  - RANGE liveness GC TTL: 600 seconds (10 minutes)\n  - system.public.lease:   600 seconds (10 minutes)\n  - Statement/transaction statistics tables: 3600 seconds (1 hour)\n  - tenant_usage:          7200 seconds (2 hours)\n\n6. NON-DEFAULT TUNING SUMMARY\n-------------------------------\nThe following non-default configurations were detected:\n\n  a) kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate = 1.0 MiB\n     (Default: 8 MiB — intentionally throttled, likely to limit rebalance\n     impact during production workloads)\n\n  b) diagnostics.reporting.enabled = true\n     (Default: false in some versions — verify acceptability with data governance)\n\n  c) No custom zone configurations on user-defined schemas or tables were found.\n     All zone configurations present are CockroachDB system range defaults.\n\n7. AUDIT METHODOLOGY\n---------------------\n  - Read-only inspection only; no cluster configuration was modified.\n  - Data sources:\n      kubectl exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach node status --insecure\n      cockroach sql: SELECT FROM crdb_internal.cluster_settings WHERE value != default_value\n      cockroach sql: SELECT FROM crdb_internal.zones\n      kubectl get statefulset crdb-cluste